description:
A DLC pack for GROOVE COASTER WAI WAI PARTY!!!! that includes 10 Vocaloid songs, navigators, and avatars!

This pack includes the following content.
■Song Pack (10 songs)
・Servant of Evil
・Iroha Uta
・Just Be Friends
・Remote Control
・Amanojaku
・39 Music!
・Jailbreak
・Junky Night Town Orchestra
・KING
・???(Secret)

■Navigator
・Rin Kagamine *with voice
・Len Kagamine *with voice

■Avatar
・RIN(Append,2D)
・LEN(Append,2D)
・RIN(Princess,2D)
・LEN(Servant,2D)
・RIN&LEN(2D)

*Some content will be unlocked via missions after downloading.
name: VOCALOID Pack 5
